Optimize Legibility for Chrome enhances the typography of any page by inserting a simple CSS statement.

author: John Michel http://cowbird.org
 
inspiration: Jim Ray's Keming Safari Extension.. this way Chrome can keep up with the Joneses
			 http://jimray.tumblr.com/post/755083491/keming-a-safari-extension-to-fix-typography
			
